results.description:
• What we'll do
After big success in Amsterdam, we do not want to leave other Dutch cities behind! As next our foreign speakers will travel to The Hague Tech to tell you more about how can blockchain empower philanthropy or how does it relate to AI. Also our partner Komodo will present - Komodo is a unique peer-to-peer exchange platform. Don't miss out on the opportunity, review more details here https://blockchaintalks.io/our-content/upcoming-events/bctvol3-denhaag/ and get your ticket here https://www.ticketkantoor.nl/shop/bct3/en - let's create decentralized blockchain hubs also outside Amsterdam!
